text: Laibach is the debut album of the Yugoslavian (now Slovenia) industrial group Laibach. It was first released in 1985, although it was only in 1991 that it was released on CD. The tracks "Police Blow" and "First TV Generation" were composed by Laibach's sub-group 300.000 V.K.. It was released again in 1999 with additional bonus songs. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:1985 debut albums Category:Laibach (band) albums
